QuestData.Title: Rescue the Earthspeaker!
QuestData.Description: Good! You've brought allies.$b$bYou must hurry if we are to rescue Erunak.$b$bGo now. Fight your way through Neptulon's halls. Find the shaman and free him from these worms... if he still lives.$b$bDon't worry about them coming up from behind you. I'll see that nothing makes it past me!
